      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Communication:** Always approach emails and meetings with **respect** for others' time, ensuring your tone reflects our shared **professionalism**. When discussing sensitive topics, clearly define **boundaries** to prevent misunderstandings and maintain a productive atmosphere.\n\n**Personal Space:** Respect physical **boundaries** by keeping a comfortable distance during casual chats and avoiding intrusive personal questions. This simple act of **professionalism** helps everyone feel safe and focused on their work.\n\n**General Conduct:** Uphold **respect** in all interactions, from hallway greetings to virtual collaboration, by actively listening and valuing diverse perspectives. Consistently honoring **boundaries** and demonstrating **professionalism** ensures a harmonious workplace where everyone can succeed.",
      "source": "target",
